{% block form %}

  <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">You cannot claim Attendance Allowance if you get ADP</h1>

  <p class="govuk-body">If you are already getting Adult Disability Payment, 
  you are not eligible for Attendance Allowance.</p>

  <p class="govuk-body">If you submit an application for Attendance Allowance, your existing 
  benefits will be reviewed which may result in a change to what you currently get.</p>

  <p class="govuk-body"><a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.mygov.scot/adult-disability-payment">Find out more about ADP</a>, including how to 
  <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.mygov.scot/adult-disability-payment-reviews/changes-report">report a change to your care needs or circumstances</a>.</p>

